#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Remember, when we practice responding calmly and sharing how we feel, our teens learn to do the same. This skill will help them their whole life!"
msgstr "Kumbuka, tunapojizoesha kujibu kwa utulivu na kushirikishana jinsi tunavyohisi, vijana wetu hujifunza kufanya vivyo hivyo. Ustadi huu utawasaidia maisha yao yote!"

#. type=data_list
