msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Hear how @data.characters.media_son_1.name learned to stay calm from his father"
msgstr "Sikia jinsi @data.characters.media_son_1.name alivyojifunza kuwa mtulivu kutoka kwa baba yake"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Whenever I would do something wrong, my father would get so angry at me and beat me. He would not even listen to me and I would get so angry as well at him and everyone else.\n"
"\n"
"Now, when he gets angry, he first takes a few deep breaths before he responds. It makes everyone calm down instead of causing a big fight.\n"
"\n"
"It really helped me at home and at school, because even me I am no longer slashing everyone and I am no longer this moody person. When I feel really angry or stressed, I also take deep breaths like my father does. I am a different person."
msgstr ""
"Pindi nilipofanya kitu kibaya, Baba yangu alinikasirikia sana na kunipiga. Alikuwa hanisikilizi na hii ilinifanya kumkasirikia yeye pamoja na watu wengine.\n"
"\n"
"Sasa, pindi anapokuwa na hasira, anachukua dakika chache kuvuta pumzi ndefu kabla hajajibu chochote. Inafanya kila mtu kutulia badala ya kusababisha ugomvi mkubwa.\n"
"\n"
"Hii inanisaidia sana nyumbani na hata shuleni, hata Mimi sasa siwakasirikii wengine na si mtu wa hisia kali. Pindi ninapojihisi hasira au mwenye msongo wa mawazo, Navuta pumzi ndefu kama Baba yangu anavyofanya. Nimekuwa mtu tofauti."

